<h5>
    "At Rest"
</h5>

<p class = 'definition'>
    When a problem says something is <strong>at rest</strong>,
    it means that velocity is equal to zero.
    If it <strong>begins at rest</strong>, initial velocity is zero.
    If the <strong>ends at rest</strong>, final velocity is zero.
</p>

